  • クラスのサマリー 
    クラス 説明
    FujiStaticCorrection
    This class computes values of Static correction after Fuji et al., (2010)
    dataselectionした後のフォルダでやる
    The time shift value t for the ray path is for the observed timewindow.
    MomentTensor
    Moment Tensor
    Global CMT 1:Mrr 2:Mtt 3:Mpp 4:M rt 5:Mrp 6 Mtp
    DSM 1:Mrr 2:Mrt 3:Mrp 4:Mtt 5:M tp 6:Mpp This class is IMMUTABLE.
    SCARDEC
    This class is IMMUTABLE.
    SCARDEC.SCARDEC_ID
    ID for information
    SourceTimeFunction
    Source time function.
    SourceTimeFunctionByStackedPeaks
    Source time function estimation by stacked peaks.
    StaticCorrection
    Static correction data for a raypath.
    StaticCorrectionFile
    Information File of StaticCorrection 1 time shift 17 byte The file contains
    Numbers of stations, events
    Each station information
    - name, network, position
    Each event
    - Global CMT ID Each period
    Each static correction information
    - see in StaticCorrectionFile.read(Path)
    TakeuchiStaticCorrection
    Maker of static correction suggested by Nozomu Takeuchi.
